# Contact form (Web3Forms) — required for the /contact form to actually
# deliver messages to the company inbox.
#
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com
# 2. Enter the company email (e.g. Info@ecologic-circle.com) to create an
#    access key — the key is emailed to you instantly, no account needed.
# 3. Copy the key below (local dev), AND add the same variable in Vercel:
#    Project → Settings → Environment Variables.
#
# Messages submitted through the contact form are delivered to whichever
# inbox owns this key.
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
